					"value": "<p>Eldeghant makes a wide, arcing swing. Make a single melee Strike and compare the attack roll result to the ACs of up to two foes, each of whom must be within his melee reach and adjacent to the other. Roll damage only once and apply it to each creature he hit. A Swipe counts as two attacks for Eldeghant's multiple attack penalty.</p><p></p>",
